---
title: Crispy Maple-Mustard Chicken with Roasted Potato Wedges & Carrots
description: Some say crispy panko-coated chicken is pretty tough to top. Those people clearly don’t know our chefs. They went and made crispy chicken 25x (a scientific number) more delicious by drizzling it with a lick-your-plate-style maple and mustard sauce. On the side, there’s seasoned potato wedges and crispy-edged roasted carrots. The best part? Everything comes together on one baking sheet in under 40 minutes. Because couldn’t we all use a little more time (and much fewer dishes to wash)?
